   International:
   World Wire
   ----
   Compiled by William Mathewson
</HL>
<DATE>
09/11/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A18
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP U.EPF RD SC C.BIM PEP FREST LATAM SANYY G.SIE
</CO>
<IN>
AIRLINES (AIR)
RESTAURANTS, FAST-FOOD, CATERING (RES)
