<LP>
   AT&amp;T Capital Corp. said it purchased U.S. Instrument
Rentals Inc., a subsidiary of Ford Motor Co.'s U.S. Leasing
International unit. Terms weren't disclosed.
   The financing unit of American Telephone &amp; Telegraph Co.,
