</IN>
<LP>
   ENVIRONMENTAL DIAGNOSTICS Inc. (Burlington, N.C.) --
William Eastham resigned for personal reasons from the board
of this maker of human-clinical and agricultural diagnostic
tests.
</LP>
<TEXT>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
